  "title": "ISic001343. Epitaph for Agathe",
  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Marta Fogagnolo</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-text=\"Ἐνθάδε\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"ἐνθάδε\">[Ἐ]νθάδε</span>  <span data-text=\"κῖτε\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"κεῖμαι\">κῖτε</span>  <br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ἀγάθη\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἀγάθη\"><span data-text=\"Ἀγάθη\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"Ἀγάθη\">Ἀγάθη</span></span></span>  <span data-text=\"ἐτέων\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"ἔτος\">ἐτέων</span>  <br id=\"al3-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span><span dir=\"ltr\">(vac.4)</span>  <span data-text=\"μ\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"μ\">μ</span>´ <span dir=\"ltr\">(vac.4)</span>  <br id=\"al4-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span><span data-text=\"πρὸ\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"πρό\">πρὸ</span>  <span dir=\"ltr\">(vac.1)</span>  <span data-text=\"ζ\" data-n=\"50\" data-lemma=\"ζ\">ζ</span>´ <span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"καλαν\n                    δῶν\"><span data-text=\"καλαν\n                    δῶν\" data-n=\"55\" data-lemma=\"Kalendae\">καλαν-<br id=\"al5-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span>δῶν</span></span>  <span data-text=\"Σεπτε\n                    βρί☧ωνΣεπτεμβρίων\" data-n=\"60\" data-lemma=\"September\">Σεπτε-<br id=\"al6-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">6</span>β̣ρί☧ων</span>  </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\">l.5 reg., orig. ΣΕΠΤΕ ΒΡΙ☧ΩΝΣεπτε βρί☧ων</p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Dmitry Dundua, Robert Crellin</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive-simple-lemmatized\">  <div class=\"textpart\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <span data-text=\"Ἐνθάδε\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"ἐνθάδε\">Ἐνθάδε</span>  <span data-text=\"κῖτε\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"κεῖμαι\">κῖτε</span>  <span data-text=\"Ἀγάθη\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"Ἀγάθη\">Ἀγάθη</span>  <span data-text=\"ἐτέων\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"ἔτος\">ἐτέων</span>  <span dir=\"ltr\">(vac.4)</span>  <span data-text=\"μ\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"μ\">μ</span>  <span dir=\"ltr\">(vac.4)</span>  <span data-text=\"πρὸ\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"πρό\">πρὸ</span>  <span dir=\"ltr\">(vac.1)</span>  <span data-text=\"ζ\" data-n=\"50\" data-lemma=\"ζ\">ζ</span>  <span data-text=\"καλανδῶν\" data-n=\"55\" data-lemma=\"Kalendae\">καλανδῶν</span>  <span data-text=\"Σεπτεμβρίων\" data-n=\"60\" data-lemma=\"September\">Σεπτεμβρίων</span>  </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Marta Fogagnolo</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-text=\"Ἐνθάδε\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"ἐνθάδε\">[.]ΝΘΑΔΕ</span><span data-text=\"κῖτε\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"κεῖμαι\">ΚΙΤΕ</span><br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ἀγάθη\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἀγάθη\"><span data-text=\"Ἀγάθη\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"Ἀγάθη\">ΑΓΑΘΗ</span></span></span><span data-text=\"ἐτέων\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"ἔτος\">ΕΤΕΩΝ</span><br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span data-text=\"μ\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"μ\">Μ</span> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br id=\"al4-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span><span data-text=\"πρὸ\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"πρό\">ΠΡΟ</span> &nbsp;&nbsp; <span data-text=\"ζ\" data-n=\"50\" data-lemma=\"ζ\">Ζ</span><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"καλαν\n                    δῶν\"><span data-text=\"καλαν\n                    δῶν\" data-n=\"55\" data-lemma=\"Kalendae\">ΚΑΛΑΝ<br id=\"al5-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span>ΔΩΝ</span></span><span data-text=\"Σεπτε\n                    βρί☧ωνΣεπτεμβρίων\" data-n=\"60\" data-lemma=\"September\">ΣΕΠΤΕ<br id=\"al6-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">6</span>.ΡΙ☧ΩΝ</span></span></div><p class=\"miniapp\">l.5 reg., orig. ΣΕΠΤΕ ΒΡΙ☧ΩΝΣεπτε βρί☧ων</p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Dmitry Dundua, Robert Crellin</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic-simple-lemmatized\"><div class=\"textpart\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><span data-text=\"Ἐνθάδε\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"ἐνθάδε\">ΕΝΘΑΔΕ</span><span data-text=\"κῖτε\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"κεῖμαι\">ΚΙΤΕ</span><span data-text=\"Ἀγάθη\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"Ἀγάθη\">ΑΓΑΘΗ</span><span data-text=\"ἐτέων\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"ἔτος\">ΕΤΕΩΝ</span> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span data-text=\"μ\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"μ\">Μ</span> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span data-text=\"πρὸ\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"πρό\">ΠΡΟ</span> &nbsp;&nbsp; <span data-text=\"ζ\" data-n=\"50\" data-lemma=\"ζ\">Ζ</span><span data-text=\"καλανδῶν\" data-n=\"55\" data-lemma=\"Kalendae\">ΚΑΛΑΝΔΩΝ</span><span data-text=\"Σεπτεμβρίων\" data-n=\"60\" data-lemma=\"September\">ΣΕΠΤΕΜΒΡΙΩΝ</span></span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2><a href=\"ISic001343_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic001343_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic001343.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic001343-thumb.jpg\"></a></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span>  <span>Text based photographs</span>  </span>; </li><li><span class=\"2\">2: <span> Kirchhoff: ἐτ&lt;ων&gt;ν </span>  </span><br></li><li><span class=\"3\">3: <span>Kirchhoff: ἐτε]λ[εύτησεν τῇ; Kaibel, Wessel: λα (vel μ); Torremuzza, Ferrara, Libertini, Ferrua; Korhonen: μ</span>  </span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>English translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a href=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0001-7077-0703\">Alex Antoniou</a></p>  <p>Here lies Agathe, of 40 years, (passed away) 7 days before the Kalends of September.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>Italian translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0001-5187-5163\">Marta Fogagnolo</a></p>  <p>Qui giace Agathe, di 40 anni, (morta) 7 giorni prima delle Kalende di Settembre.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>The structure of the epitaph is frequent in the Christian age. The name of the deceased recurs in some Paleochristian epitaphs from Catania, such as IG 14.524 = <a href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic001344\" target=\"_blank\">ISic001344</a>, IG 14.525 = <a href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic000964\" target=\"_blank\">ISic000964</a>, IG 14.552 = <a href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic001371\" target=\"_blank\">ISic001371</a>. Kirchhoff’s supplement at l. 3 <span class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">ἐτε]λ[εύτησεν τῇ</span> does not seem to be necessary (moreover, there is not a lacuna at this line): even if the verb <span class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">τελευτάω</span> is frequent in this formula after the indication of the years and before the indication of the day of death, a similar structure without the verb <span class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">τελευτάω</span> recurs also in IGCVO 1380 (Rome). The indication of the day of death as <span class=\"lang\" lang=\"la\">dies natalis</span> is common in Christian epitaphs.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> 1379 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000394\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000394</a>  </li><li> Castelli 1769 242 no.9 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002084\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002084</a>  </li><li> Castelli 1784 258 no.9 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002083\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002083</a>  </li><li> Ferrara 1829 366 no.4 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002005\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002005</a>  </li><li> Kirchhoff 1877 9480 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001249\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001249</a>  </li><li> Kaibel 1890 <a href=\"https://clio.columbia.edu/catalog/6873760\" target=\"_blank\">523</a>  <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072</a>  </li><li> Libertini 1930 318 no.9 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001871\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001871</a>  </li><li> Ferrua 1989 no.434 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001995\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001995</a>  </li><li> Korhonen 2004 172 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028</a>  </li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> <p>Irregular letters: lunate Ε and Σ, cursive Μ and Ω. Α, Δ and Λ with accentuated upper serifs. Chi-Rho symbol in the middle of l. 6.</p> Lines 1-6  10-30  Interlineation line 1 to 2  not recorded  </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. </div>",
